{"tid":2182870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(禁藥撚) 點解要禁人食藥比賽?","createTime":"2020-08-31T14:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T23:15:44.000Z","uid":223256,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"32c9c63391920422e1ab1b743f507953be9ed23d","tid":2182870,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"禁人食藥本身就係反人類行為<br />\n要禁食藥、咁洗唔洗禁補品禁紅牛?<br />\n食左藥跑步做運動後<br />\n都係自己跑自己郁<br />\n都無用工具<br />\n點解要禁?<br />\n只要運動員同團隊覺得需要<br />\n咪大家一齊食囉<br />\n我樂意見到人類用藥物催谷體能<br />\n跑100米突破9秒內成積喎"},{"pid":"d8fe26fc54ffc7046cc4675d12b986fe1b48ff3e","tid":2182870,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"明面禁止啫"},{"pid":"d88615f9974905ffbcaf3263c67ef0d91e21b823","tid":2182870,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"尿紫咁耐都未有聲氣<br />\n禁撚左佢未"},{"pid":"2d5238d2a270bfd948a5890670ca63c614753e85","tid":2182870,"uid":18241,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"其實分開黎比賽就攪掂<br />\n<br />\n一邊全部食藥<br />\n<br />\n一邊全部唔食藥<br />\n<br />\n各有各比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eb390ad79e8a040e3830db2deb210e84be651e","tid":2182870,"uid":311,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"驚比大國屈哂機<br />\n窮既國家整藥技術無咁勁"},{"pid":"5d5e0930fd70ba041f30a734a2c118658017e278","tid":2182870,"uid":39508,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"食到魔鬼隊咁點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2c8dbdc43e5ada9a965f96ee4bc52fa4a1eb88","tid":2182870,"uid":223256,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"5d5e0930fd70ba041f30a734a2c118658017e278","tid":2182870,"uid":39508,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"食到魔鬼隊咁點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"